text:
tears flow in kansas,
the chiefs lost in the super bowl,
i am now at peace

bad bunny is on,
the world listens carefully,
you get the message?

snow has stopped falling,
is it time for some juice yet?
let's just go on home

meep moop bop peep boop,
i am a regular cat,
with more than nine lives

i am octoprince,
look at my new shiny sword
or check out my hat
